        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>browned chicken</strong> with the<strong> stuffing mixture</strong>,<strong> </strong>then press it down gently to coat the surface of the chicken</p><p>Transfer the<strong> sausage stuffing topped chicken</strong> to the other side of the baking tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 12-14 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the juices run clear</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>chicken</strong> to a clean board and leave to rest for a couple of min before slicing</p>",
      "order": 5,
